</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>BMW THE X3 及 X4 到港　香港價錢 + 荃灣新陳列室登場</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/11/bmw-the-x3x4/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=bmw-the-x3x4</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 11 Feb 2022 08:10:41 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[EDITOR’S 推介]]></category><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[bmw]]></category><category><![CDATA[BMW THE X3]]></category><category><![CDATA[BMW THE X4]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1085815</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>自 2003 年首款 BMW X3 亮相以來，BMW 豪華運動休旅 SAV (Sports Activity  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>自 2003 年首款 BMW X3 亮相以來，BMW 豪華運動休旅 SAV (Sports Activity Vehicle) 都頗受香港歡迎。是次 BMW Hong Kong 引入了多達十種不同版本的 X3 及 X4 新車，滿足車迷不同需要。當中全新 X3 xDrive20i、X4 xDrive20i ，以及 <span lang="EN-US">BMW THE 2 Coup</span>é 及 <span lang="EN-US">THE 4 Coup</span>é 更是首度於全新升級的 BMW 荃灣陳列室亮相。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1085836" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143741-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143741-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143741-2-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143741-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143741-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143741-2-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143741-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>棱角分明的時尚外型</h2><p>全新 BMW X3 與 BMW X4 車身設計上加入了大量凌厲的骨線，大幅強化運動與跑感氣息。透過更立體且具侵略性的線條，加上標誌性雙腎形鬼面罩與全新設計上下分割的六角型頭燈及燻黑的立體尾燈，大大提升了辨識度。標準配備智慧型轉向式 LED 頭燈結合車頭重新設計的 Air Curtain 進氣口，勾勒出越野車的攝人樣貌。而全新 BMW X4 更完美平衡豪華跑車與運動休旅車的設計特質，以流線型的車身線條展現動感十足的轎跑曲線，搭配專屬網狀鬼面罩設計，及立體 L 型尾燈。標準配備 19 吋輕合金輪圈，M Sport 版本加入了 M Sport 擾流部件及 M 專屬車側徽章。而 X3 M40i 與 X4 M40i 則配以 20 吋 M 輕合金輪圈與 M Performance 擾流部件打造，包括首次於 ＭPerformance 系列出現的 M 專屬亮黑色雙桿式雙腎形鬼面罩、M 專屬勾型側鏡設計，車尾兩邊單出矩形排氣喉及擾流裝置，突出了 BMW M 的競賽氣息。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1085821 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424716_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-694x512.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="512" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424716_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-694x512.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424716_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-1221x900.jpg 1221w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424716_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-768x566.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424716_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-1536x1133.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424716_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-2048x1510.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424716_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲BMW THE X3</p><h2>搭載全新升級 iDrive７系統</h2><p>以駕駛者導向的中控台，一直都是 BMW 標誌性的設計，至今亦未曾改變傳承經典的堅持，標準配備的 12.3 吋電子儀表板以及增大至 12.3 吋的中央顯示屏配合 BMW Intelligent Personal Assistant，簡單的指令即可操控。搭載全新升級 iDrive７系統除了提供原廠導航系統外，更支援 Remote Software Upgrade 遠端軟體升級科技，車主不再需要特地回維修中心便能直接與雲端串連，就如同目前眾人所熟悉的智慧型手機軟體更新方式，直接為自己的愛車進行系統更新。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1085827 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424690_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424690_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424690_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424690_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424690_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424690_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424690_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲BMW THE X3</p><p>全新 BMW X3 與 BMW X4 車廂材質鋪陳是配合熱愛戶外運動或是與家人暢遊需要全車座以 Sensatec 透氣材質打造，儀錶檯以 Sensatec 人造皮質包覆，前座運動型座椅，標準配備全景觀天窗，視野更遼闊。標準版本用上多功能真皮軚環與黑色高光澤飾板，M Sport 版本搭配 M 多功能真皮軚環與碳黑鋁質格紋飾板；M40i 更升級 Vernasca 真皮運動型座椅，搭配 M 多功能真皮方向盤、碳黑鋁質格紋飾板與 Harman Kardon 音響系統，營造細膩舒適的車廂佈局。後座採用 40/20/40 獨立覆摺後座椅背，高靈活性運用讓全新 X3 空間進一步擴大至最高 1,600Ｌ。標準配備 Comfort Access 免鑰匙系統及感應式電動尾門系統，兼顧運動型豪華休旅車用家實際需要，和駕駛樂趣。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1085822 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424692_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424692_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424692_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-1280x852.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424692_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-768x511.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424692_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424692_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-2048x1363.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424692_highRes_the-new-bmw-x3-xdriv-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲BMW THE X3</p><p>全新 BMW X3 與 X4 搭載 BMW TwinPower Turbo 汽油引擎和 8 前速 Steptronic 自動波箱，導入 48V Mild Hybrid 油電輕混能技術，藉以強化動力表現，可於急速加速時啟動 eBoost 功能額外增加 11hp 馬力輔助，減少廢氣排放之餘，成就高性能與卓越燃油效益，和舒適的操控及愜意舒適駕乘體驗。四輪驅動的全新 BMW X3 與 X4，xDrive20i 型號擁有 184hp 最大馬力和 300Nm 峰值扭力；xDrive 30i 型號則擁有 252hp 最大馬力和 350Nm 峰值扭力。X3 M40i 型號、X4 M40i 型號則是搭載 M 部門調校的 BMW M TwinPower Turbo  三公升直列六缸汽油引擎與 8 前速 Steptronic 自動波箱，擁有 360hp 最大馬力及 500Nm 峰值扭力，0 到 100km/h 加速僅需 4.9 秒即可完成。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1085823 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424729_highRes_the-new-bmw-x4-m40i--694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424729_highRes_the-new-bmw-x4-m40i--694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424729_highRes_the-new-bmw-x4-m40i--768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/P90424729_highRes_the-new-bmw-x4-m40i-.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲BMW THE X4</p><p>BMW 設計了全新 BMW X3 與 X4 的底盤，50：50 前後車重比例及 xDrive 智慧型可變四輪傳動系統，能根據路況以 0~100% 的比例彈性分配前後軸驅動力，輔以 DSC 動態穩定控制系統，提升駕駛安全性同時更能提供樂趣的駕馭體驗。BMW X4 M40i 更加入 M Sport Differential 電子差速器，有助於過彎時更有效加速，抓地力更強。標準配備 BMW Personal CoPilot 智慧駕駛輔助系統，透過盲點偵測警示、主動防撞輔助系統與行人偵測、車道偏離警示、後方車流警示、後方防追撞警示等系統的確保行車安全穩定性,安全防護如影隨形。除了駕駛輔助，更加入 BMW 獨有的 50 米倒車輔助功能  (Reversing Assistant)，全方位為車主護航，以最舒適且安全的方式引領您抵達目的地。</p><p>新推出 My BMW App，用家能透過智能手機內的應用程式，遙距控制車輛的各種功能。例如用家在酷熱的天氣下，預先啟動送風功能，降低車廂溫度。此外，車主亦可透過 My BMW App 查看汽車位置、汽車狀態，以及遙距控制功能等等，方便車主隨時隨地實時、快速和簡單地控制新車。</p><p style="text-align: left;">BMW THE X3 售價：HK$<span lang="EN-GB">539,000 </span><span lang="ZH-HK">起</span><br />BMW THE X4 售價：HK$<span lang="EN-GB">$589,000 </span><span lang="ZH-HK">起</span></p><h2>BMW 荃灣陳列室全面升級</h2><p>另外，BMW 荃灣陳列室已作全面升級，逾 3 萬呎的廣闊空間，４大區域包括 Café Corner、VIP Lounge、M Corner &amp; Delivery Room、BMW Service Centre，以及３大專區包括 BMW SAV X 系專區，M 系專區，及 I 系專區。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1085847 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143552-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143552-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143552-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143552-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143552-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143552-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143552-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新 BMW 荃灣陳列室除了涵蓋一系列硬件上的升級外，４款 BMW 運動豪華車型亦會一併於今年展出，當中包括 BMW 豪華中型 SAV 及 SAC 典範 Ｘ 系列—全新 BMW THE X3 及 BMW THE X4，iX3 純電休旅車亦於同日率先公開發佈正式售價及接受訂金。亦會展示全新，一代 BMW THE 2 Coupé 和全新 BMW THE 4 Gran Coupé。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1085830 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_144123-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_144123-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_144123-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_144123-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_144123-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_144123-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_144123-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1085832 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_144043-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_144043-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_144043-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_144043-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_144043-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_144043-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_144043-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1085833 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_1440530-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_1440530-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_1440530-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_1440530-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_1440530-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_1440530-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_1440530-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><u>Café Corner</u></h2><p>於全面升級的 BMW 荃灣陳列室之中，除了展現 BMW 最新資訊及品牌理念訊息的陳設外，還新增了木色主調配上白色及燈光點綴的 BMW Café Corner。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1085829 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_153235-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_153235-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_153235-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_153235-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_153235-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_153235-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_153235-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲BMW Café Corner</p><h2><u>VIP Lounge</u></h2><p>於 VIP Lounge 內，客人可一邊喝咖啡，一邊聆聽 BMW 專員的講解。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1085831 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143804-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143804-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143804-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143804-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143804-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143804-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/20220210_143804-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲VIP Lounge</p><h2><u>M Corner </u><u>及車輛交付專區</u></h2><p>全港首個 ///Ｍ Corner 專區全面展現 BMW ///M 系跑車的家族設計，將高效能的 BMW 產品展出。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1085846 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/273014148_4674883955968377_3281580364836552310_n-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/273014148_4674883955968377_3281580364836552310_n-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/273014148_4674883955968377_3281580364836552310_n-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/273014148_4674883955968377_3281580364836552310_n.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新 BMW 荃灣陳列室詳情：</p><p>開放時間：9:00am &#8211; 7:00pm (星期一至六)；10:00am &#8211; 7:00pm (星期日及公眾假期)</p><p>電話： 31936888</p><p>地點：荃灣青山公路荃灣段 380 號</p></p><div class="feedflare">
